{"type": "article", "id": 57132, "title": "可重复使用的硅胶食器，也可以用作洗漱包｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-10-09T22:49:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 15888, "name": "本土创造"}, {"id": 28788, "name": "失物招领"}, {"id": 53303, "name": "Finell"}, {"id": 41284, "name": "蔡烈超"}, {"id": 53304, "name": "Yosuke Matsushita"}, {"id": 53305, "name": "Yuming Hu"}, {"id": 53306, "name": "Rebecca Finell"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 196, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181009201656ELSyN6xrRbslFoQf.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #5a5a5a; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #5a5a5a} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #3498db; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #3498db} </style>  </p><p class=\"\">「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Zip Top by Rebecca Finell </h3><p>很多城市开始推出限塑政策，从自备购物袋到禁用塑料吸管等等。民众开始意识到塑料垃圾对环境带来的破坏。高端家居用品品牌 FINELL 的创始人 Rebecca Finell 最近推出了一款硅胶容器 Zip Top，看起来有点像是结合了被子和塑料袋，平坦的底部配上可以密封的封口，坚固且能重复使用，能够取代家中常见的拉链塑料保鲜盒。</p><p>Zip Top 被称为使用了最高等级的硅胶，不含 BPA、铅和 PVC，可以放在冰箱、冷冻库、洗碗机、微波炉和烤箱，耐高温，食物放在里面，不用担心有害物质渗入其中。</p><p>平时除了可以储存食物外，还可以拿来当成便当盒、点心袋，或是用来收纳洗漱用品等小物件。目前，它在众筹网站 kickstarter 上的售价为 28 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1246120690/zip-top-reusable-containers-stand-up-stay-open-and?ref=7v3z8z\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201753b8Ql7pCf4qP9FoBL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810092017536ahoDAUmkqENdfTw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810092017547lzGfkZ2ei9FLmaH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201754k49oVyiMgDdcbN8R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201754Nt3UDEmAedO1XBiR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201754C896ngx2NbVr0PHd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201755mbfSKnJ7WPxIEC1c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://ziptop.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Finell</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>A Range of Chairs for he restless body by Yuming Hu</h3><p>清华大学环境艺术设计系刚刚毕业的学生 Yuming Hu，设计了一系列特殊的椅子，专注于人们微妙细小的肢体语言和姿势。</p><p>“微动机一直被认为是心理学的一个重要组成部分，但是在座椅设计领域似乎没有被特别重视。” Yuming Hu 表示。在他看来，大多数椅子只考虑到符合人体工程学的基本需求，但其实可以深入到更“具体”的设计，比如人们坐着时如何有意识地伸展上肢、手、下肢、脚和躯干，有的设有垂直向外延伸的臂，有的设有钢琴踏板一样的装置。</p><p>这一系列椅子最近刚刚在北京国际设计周上展出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201851Jnc6pEBAdCwDvsxU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810092018529cleQs13RkMXLmSv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745770\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810092018520YzhteF2VsEXAGoR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.353215\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201853nma7KhzBLQlbO3HA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.340525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201854b1luXcPnHBiWmd34.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.345601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201855LnGjeDdzPk8BREl7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.345178\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/10/08/yuming-hu-chairs-restless-body-singhua-university-furniture-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Colonia by Yosuke Matsushita</h3><p>Colonia 是日本设计师 Yosuke Matsushita 最新推出的新项目，他将海绵浸入熔化的树脂中创造出一种新的固体材料。</p><p>这是一系列独特的饰品盒，表面的纹理非常多样化。在他看来，市面上类似的产品同质化的情况很严重，我们被大量这一类的产品包围。但 Yosuke Matsushita 认为，他想借助 Colonia 这个项目展示出多样化的制作体验、产品的质地、香味和色调，使得我们的生活更加丰富多彩，增强我们对周围世界的感知能力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810092019529uNxOt26zsnSVBXf.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201952qAh3MZXRmJSHIbdx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201952Uj2TcRiEWatly0GO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201952z8VZDAdCNS41iW30.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201952jv6hfOFg3AVMsSDC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201952mKw3iGUZbLh9z7Tr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201953ExMWYsmyi79lgH3U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009201953NJDHfX3uki7nW5be.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/yosuke-matsushita-colonia-melted-resin-sponges-10-08-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>CO/RE collection by  Mario Tsai for Lost &amp; Found</h3><p>CO/RE 是蔡烈超工作室为原创家具品牌失物招领设计的新系列。</p><p>设计师沿着传统工艺的脉络，以家居设计为核心，探索现代审美的更多表现可能。以 CO/RE 系列为支点，失物招领把关注的目光从“家”延展到文创空间、设计工作室、艺廊画廊等多种多样的现代生活场域，这也是失物招领成立 10 年后的又一次全新尝试。</p><p>伍德茶几是把一块方形木头放大，一块长方木头从桌面底部直接穿过，简洁干练，稳定而又踏实。琼脂沙发拥有让人记忆深刻的饱满弧度，坐感 Q 弹，由 6 个不同尺寸的功能模块组成，系统的尺寸及结构设计，可以提供双人、多人及拐角空间的解决方案，使空间更具表现力和搭配力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009202031Zr0COmNQ32W5GEFn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009202031k5AyHUFVbDjMSzof.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009202032KH70LmE2in6QSPXO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009202032vTEyoAQeZOiLl9zJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009202032WulSBvMF53VtZHos.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.mariotsai.studio/core/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mario Tsai</a></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009202031Ffk8Nc2GYIzxAhyU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>水磨石系列 工 1000 圆桌 by 本土创造</h3><p>独立设计品牌本土创造推出水磨石系列新品工 1000 圆桌，圆与直线、块与面的碰撞很特别。</p><p>圆桌以石材回收边角料为骨料，水磨石桌面自然散布黑白两色原生石料，在黑色或白色的底色上裸露粗犷的自然。</p><p>桌墩的八边形柱体，同样是建筑中常见的元素，充斥极大部分视觉的平行棱边与方正体块，在悬空极薄的面板与坚实的地面之间，给出理性、稳定的连接。直径一米的桌面满足 3 至 4 人就餐使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009202118ioa3F5wt0IkWGPbs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499167\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009202118T7XNRxqHInFyfUaS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009202118kto5se8nSxlNdT3w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810092021185KAX2W0oM7PYetHi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181009202119sxw7yoi1LbhOtDgA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.bentudesign.com/CN/pviews.asp?b_classid=130&amp;yid=50\" rel=\"nofollow\">本土创造</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}